<p>The <code>BreadcrumbList</code> renders an <code>&lt;ol&gt;</code>
  that holds the ancestor trail. It should be used inside a
  <a href="/components/breadcrumb-nav/">BreadcrumbNav</a> so assistive
  tech has a navigation landmark.</p>

<p>See the <a href="/components/breadcrumb-nav/">BreadcrumbNav demo</a>
  for usage.</p>
